name: MALOU
description: In the bustling world of cryptocurrency, where innovation and creativity intersect, emerges MALOU — a Blockchain meme project deeply rooted in the industrious spirit of the monkey. With the native token “NEVER,” MALOU endeavors to harness luck on the journey to success. This white paper outlines the vision, mechanics, and distribution strategy of MALOU, positioning it as a vibrant and engaging addition to the Binance Smart Chain (BSC) ecosystem.
